  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Appointment
    Represents an appointment between a patient and a doctor in the hospital system.
    AppointmentOutcomeRecord
    Represents an appointment outcome record, which contains information about the outcome of an appointment, including consultation notes, service type, and prescriptions.
    MedicalRecord
    Represents the medical record of a patient, which contains information such as diagnoses and treatment plans.
    Medicine
    Represents a Medicine record, which contains information about the medicine's name, current stock, and alert threshold for replenishment.
    Prescription
    Represents a prescription for a specific medicine with details including medicine name, prescribed amount, and the status of the prescription.
    Record
    Represents an abstract record with a unique identifier.
    ReplenishmentRequest
    Represents a replenishment request for a specific medicine.
